Class OMRSRESTRepositoryConnector

All Implemented Interfaces:
AuditLoggingComponent, SecureConnectorExtension, OMRSMetadataCollectionManager
public class OMRSRESTRepositoryConnector extends OMRSRepositoryConnector
The OMRSRESTRepositoryConnector is a connector to a remote Apache Atlas repository (or any other metadata repository that supports the OMRS REST APIs). This is the connector used by the EnterpriseOMRSRepositoryConnector to make a direct call to another open metadata repository.
